        <h2>Not what you expected?</h2>

        <p>The debian.ch association was founded in November 2006 and could
        obtain the debian.ch domain on 15.12.2006 from <a
        href="http://www.cril.ch/">CRIL / Marc Schaefer</a>. debian.ch
        does not sell Debian CDs, but its previous owner continues to do so;
        please contact them at <a
        href="mailto:debian-cd-sales&#37;&#52;&#48;cril&#46;ch">debian-cd-sales<span>&#64;</span>cril<span>&#46;</span>ch</a>.</p>
